LYRICS :

മംഗല നാള് മംഗല നാള്
ഇണക്കുരുവികൾക്ക് മൊഞ്ചിലിന്ന് മംഗല നാള്  (തൻസീർ )

കൊട്ടും പാട്ടും മേളമോടെ വെട്ടമിന്നിതാ
മങ്കകൾ കരങ്ങൾ തട്ടി ചുറ്റുകൂടിതാ  (താജുദ്ധീൻ )

ചെക്കനരികെ പെണ്ണിരുന്നു നാണമോടിതാ (അത്തു )

ഹഖിലിന്ന് വന്നു ചേർന്നതൊക്കെയിന്നിതാ (നിസാം )

സൊറയും കളി ചിരിയും (മെഹ്രുന്നീസ )
കഥ പറയും മധു നിറയും (വിസ്മയ )

അതിലു മൃദുല മധുര ചിന്ത മിഥുനങ്ങൾക്കിതാ (സ്വിഫ്രാൻ, ഫിസ്ര )

മംഗല നാള് മംഗല നാള് ഇണക്കുരുവികൾക്ക് മൊഞ്ചിലിന്ന് മംഗല നാള് (സഹറാൻ , നൂറിൻ )

വെള്ളി നിലാവ് പൊന്നിൻ കിനാവ് പെണ്ണെ നീയൊരു പൂവ് (താജുദ്ധീൻ )
പൂവല് മെയ്യില് മൈലാഞ്ചി ചോപ്പില് മഞ്ചം നിറയെ വിരിക്കല് (നിസാം )

തട്ടമിട്ട ഹൂറിമാര് തൊട്ടടുത്തിതാ
തൊട്ടുരുമ്മി ചാരെ നിന്റെ ചെക്കനിന്നിതാ ( തൻസീർ )

മിന്നി മാഞ്ഞിതാ നിന്റെ പൂമുഖത്തെടി
മെല്ലെ കൊഞ്ചി വന്നത് മുഹബ്ബത്താണെടീ (അത്തു )

പല വർണ്ണ പന്തലിൽ വിരിഞ്ഞ പുഞ്ചിരി(ഫിസ്ര )
പതിനാലാം രാവു തോറ്റു പോകും മഞ്ചരി(സിഫ്രാൻ )
പുലരുന്ന നാള് പുളകമല്ലേ പുന്നാരീ (വിസ്മയ, മെഹ്‌റു )

കോറസ് പല്ലവി ഫുൾ
(എല്ലാരും പാടണം )

വിണ്ണിലെ താരം മണ്ണിലിറങ്ങുന്ന മിന്നിടും മംഗല്യ നാളിതാ (വിസ്മയ )
ലങ്കിടും പൊന്നിൻ ചൊങ്കില് പെണ്ണ് മൊഞ്ചത്തിയായ് ചമഞ്ഞിതാ (അത്തു )

കനവ് കണ്ട പെണ്മണിക്ക് മാരനിന്നിതാ (മെഹറുനിസ )
കവിളിൽ പൂത്ത നാണ നുണക്കുഴി തെളിഞ്ഞിതാ (നിസാം )

പട്ടു മെത്ത കൊണ്ടലങ്കരിച്ച മണിയറ 
കൊട്ടിയടച്ചിട്ടു പുൽകിടുന്ന കലവറ (തൻസീർ )

കാത്തിരുന്ന തോഴനിന്ന് അത്തറു പൂശി ( സിഫ്രാൻ, സഹറാൻ )
ഒത്തു ചേർന്ന് പന്തലില് പുഞ്ചിരി വീശി ( ഫിസ്ര, നൂറിൻ )
ഹുസുനുൽ ജമാലിനൊത്ത ബദറുൽ മുനീറ് ( താജുദ്ധീൻ )

അതിലു മൃദുല മധുര ചിന്ത മിഥുനങ്ങൾക്കിതാ (സ്വിഫ്രാൻ, ഫിസ്ര )

മംഗല നാള് മംഗല നാള് ഇണക്കുരുവികൾക്ക് മൊഞ്ചിലിന്ന് മംഗല നാള് (സഹറാൻ , നൂറിൻ )

വെള്ളി നിലാവ് പൊന്നിൻ കിനാവ് പെണ്ണെ നീയൊരു പൂവ് (താജുദ്ധീൻ )
പൂവല് മെയ്യില് മൈലാഞ്ചി ചോപ്പില് മഞ്ചം നിറയെ വിരിക്കല് (നിസാം )

തട്ടമിട്ട ഹൂറിമാര് തൊട്ടടുത്തിതാ
തൊട്ടുരുമ്മി ചാരെ നിന്റെ ചെക്കനിന്നിതാ ( തൻസീർ )

മിന്നി മാഞ്ഞിതാ നിന്റെ പൂമുഖത്തെടി
മെല്ലെ കൊഞ്ചി വന്നത് മുഹബ്ബത്താണെടീ (അത്തു )

പല വർണ്ണ പന്തലിൽ വിരിഞ്ഞ പുഞ്ചിരി(ഫിസ്ര )
പതിനാലാം രാവു തോറ്റു പോകും മഞ്ചരി(സിഫ്രാൻ )
പുലരുന്ന നാള് പുളകമല്ലേ പുന്നാരീ (വിസ്മയ, മെഹ്‌റു )

കോറസ് പല്ലവി ഫുൾ
(എല്ലാരും പാടണം )

വിണ്ണിലെ താരം മണ്ണിലിറങ്ങുന്ന മിന്നിടും മംഗല്യ നാളിതാ (വിസ്മയ )
ലങ്കിടും പൊന്നിൻ ചൊങ്കില് പെണ്ണ് മൊഞ്ചത്തിയായ് ചമഞ്ഞിതാ (അത്തു )

കനവ് കണ്ട പെണ്മണിക്ക് മാരനിന്നിതാ (മെഹറുനിസ )
കവിളിൽ പൂത്ത നാണ നുണക്കുഴി തെളിഞ്ഞിതാ (നിസാം )

പട്ടു മെത്ത കൊണ്ടലങ്കരിച്ച മണിയറ 
കൊട്ടിയടച്ചിട്ടു പുൽകിടുന്ന കലവറ (തൻസീർ )

കാത്തിരുന്ന തോഴനിന്ന് അത്തറു പൂശി ( സിഫ്രാൻ, സഹറാൻ )
ഒത്തു ചേർന്ന് പന്തലില് പുഞ്ചിരി വീശി ( ഫിസ്ര, നൂറിൻ )
ഹുസുനുൽ ജമാലിനൊത്ത ബദറുൽ മുനീറ് ( താജുദ്ധീൻ )

snippet.title: Kamal Haasan, Suriya & Mani Ratnam |Ananda Vikatan Cinema Awards🏆 2020-21| Manikandan Clash🔥 Part 05
snippet.description:
#kamalhaasan #maniratnam #suriya #manikandan #lokeshkanagaraj  #avcinemaawards #vikatanawards #cinemavikatan #Vikatancinemaawards  

Welcome to the prestigious Vikatan Cinema Awards Function! This annual event celebrates excellence in the world of cinema, with awards being presented to the best of the best in Tamil cinema over the past three years - 2020, 2021, and 2022. Join us as we recognize the outstanding achievements of our talented actors, actresses, directors, and technicians, who have captivated audiences with their exceptional work. The awards ceremony promises to be an unforgettable evening, filled with glamour, excitement, and emotion. Watch as the winners are announced and receive their awards from our esteemed presenters. From Best Actor and Best Actress to Best Director and Best Music Director, the competition is fierce and the talent is exceptional. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy the show as we celebrate the magic of cinema and honour the best of the best at the Vikatan Cinema Awards Function.

This annual event celebrates excellence in the world of cinema, with awards being presented to the best of the best in Tamil cinema over the past three years - 2020, 2021, and 2022. Join us as we recognize the outstanding achievements of our talented actors, actresses, directors, and technicians, who have captivated audiences with their exceptional work. From Best Actor and Best Actress to Best Director and Best Music Director, the competition is fierce and the talent is exceptional. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy the show as we celebrate the magic of cinema and honour the best of the best at the Vikatan Cinema Awards Function.

From Best Actor and Best Actress to Best Director and Best Music Director, the competition is fierce and the talent is exceptional. snippet.title: Job Vs Startup: Which Way to Go? Dr. Vikas Divyakirti
snippet.description:
प्रिय व्यूअर्स,

कुछ दिन पहले दिल्ली विश्वविद्यालय के 'श्रीराम कॉलेज ऑफ कॉमर्स' के विद्यार्थियों ने अपने बिजनेस कॉन्क्लेव में आमंत्रित किया था। वहॉं की चर्चा इसी बिंदु पर केंद्रित रही कि पढ़ाई के बाद नौकरी करना बेहतर है या अपना कोई उद्यम शुरू किया जाए! इसी क्रम में यह भी बात हुई कि उद्यम ही शुरू किया जाए तो किस तरह का उद्यम अधिक उपयोगी और लाभकारी हो सकता है तथा सही निर्णय लेने के लिये किन बिंदुओं का ध्यान रखना चाहिये।


मुझे लगता है कि आपमें से ज़्यादातर लोगों के मन में भी यह दुविधा होती ही होगी, तो आज यही बातचीत आपसे साझा कर रहा हूँ। उम्मीद है कि इससे आपको अपने पेशेवर जीवन के लिये कुछ उपयोगी सूत्र मिल सकेंगे। 

शुभकामनाओं सहित, 
विकास दिव्यकीर्ति


Dear Viewers,

A few days ago, the students of Delhi University's 'Shri Ram College of Commerce' had invited me to their Business Conclave. The discussion there focused on the point that is it better to do a job after studies or to start an enterprise of your own! In the same sequence, it was also discussed that if the enterprise is started, then what kind of enterprise can be more useful and beneficial and what points should be kept in mind to take the right decision.


I think most of you must have this dilemma in your mind too, so today I am sharing this conversation with you. Hope this gives you some useful tips for your professional life.

with best wishes,
Vikas Divyakirti
tags: how to apply for a job at a startup
how to get a job at a startup with no experience
why should you pick a startup
benefits of working at a startup
Job Vs Startup by vikas divyakirti
Job Vs Startup: Which Way to Go?
What do you mean by entrepreneurship?

localized.title: Job Vs Startup: Which Way to Go? Dr. Vikas Divyakirti
localized.description:
प्रिय व्यूअर्स,

कुछ दिन पहले दिल्ली विश्वविद्यालय के 'श्रीराम कॉलेज ऑफ कॉमर्स' के विद्यार्थियों ने अपने बिजनेस कॉन्क्लेव में आमंत्रित किया था। वहॉं की चर्चा इसी बिंदु पर केंद्रित रही कि पढ़ाई के बाद नौकरी करना बेहतर है या अपना कोई उद्यम शुरू किया जाए! इसी क्रम में यह भी बात हुई कि उद्यम ही शुरू किया जाए तो किस तरह का उद्यम अधिक उपयोगी और लाभकारी हो सकता है तथा सही निर्णय लेने के लिये किन बिंदुओं का ध्यान रखना चाहिये।


मुझे लगता है कि आपमें से ज़्यादातर लोगों के मन में भी यह दुविधा होती ही होगी, तो आज यही बातचीत आपसे साझा कर रहा हूँ। उम्मीद है कि इससे आपको अपने पेशेवर जीवन के लिये कुछ उपयोगी सूत्र मिल सकेंगे। 

शुभकामनाओं सहित, 
विकास दिव्यकीर्ति


Dear Viewers,

A few days ago, the students of Delhi University's 'Shri Ram College of Commerce' had invited me to their Business Conclave. The discussion there focused on the point that is it better to do a job after studies or to start an enterprise of your own! In the same sequence, it was also discussed that if the enterprise is started, then what kind of enterprise can be more useful and beneficial and what points should be kept in mind to take the right decision.


I think most of you must have this dilemma in your mind too, so today I am sharing this conversation with you. Hope this gives you some useful tips for your professional life.

with best wishes,
Vikas Divyakirti

snippet.title: அட்சய திருதியை 2023 - செல்வ வளம் பெருக அன்று கட்டாயம் நாம் செய்ய வேண்டியது | Akshaya Tritiya 2023
snippet.description:
திருதியை திதி 22 & 23-04-2023 ஆகிய 2 தேதிகளிலும் இருப்பதால் பொருட்கள் வாங்குவது, தானம் போன்றவற்றை 22-04-2023-ஆம் தேதியிலும் செய்யலாம்.  வீடு பால் காய்ச்சுதல், வீடு குடி புகுதல், வாஸ்து போன்றவற்றை 23-04-2023 தேதியில் செய்வதே சிறந்தது.  அன்றைய தினத்திலேயே  பொருட்கள் வாங்குவது & தானம் தருதல் போன்றவற்றையும் செய்யலாம்.


அட்சய திருதியை 2022 - அன்று செய்ய வேண்டியதும், முதல் செலவாக வாங்க வேண்டியதும் | Akshaya Tritiya
https://youtu.be/VW6JZ55OkF8

அட்சய திருதியை அன்று செய்ய வேண்டிய முக்கியமான செயல்|Akshaya Tritiya| அக்ஷய திருதி
https://youtu.be/MDEbbNiG3JU

அட்சய திருதியை 2021 - இந்த முறையில் தானம் செய்தால் 100% பலன் கிடைக்கும் | Akshaya Tritiyai
https://youtu.be/YK21OQPxbl0

அனைவரும் இதனைப் பின்பற்றி பயன் பெறவும்.  மேலும் உங்கள் நண்பர்கள் மற்றும் உறவினர்களுக்கு பகிர்ந்து அவர்களுக்கும் உதவுங்கள்.

Tere Bin Episode 34 Teaser - 19th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: अतीक अशरफ मामले में एडवोकेट मनोज कुमार ने सारे संदेह उजागर कर दिए!
snippet.description:
#ateekahmad #ateequeashraf #prayagraj
Story by AR News India
 अतीक अशरफ हत्याकांड को लेकर एडवोकेट मनोज कुमार ने गंभीर सवाल उठाते हुए प्रशासन पर लापरवाही के आरोप लगाए. साथी ही पूरी घटनाक्रम से जुड़े हुए कई संदेह को उजागर करते हुए सरकार को कटघरे में खड़ा किया. इस जानकारी को लेकर आपका क्या कुछ कहना है कमेंट बॉक्स में आकर अपनी राय जरूर कीजिएगा।

Desclaimer - वीडियो में वक्ता के अपने निजी विचार है चैनल ए आर न्यूज़ इंडिया इसकी पुष्टि नहीं करता हमारा मकसद किसी भी धर्म जाति समुदाय वर्ग को ठेस पहुंचाना नहीं है।

snippet.title: Pathaan x Tiger Theme | Shah Rukh Khan, Salman Khan | Sanchit, Ankit, Julius | YRF Spy Universe
snippet.description:
With Pathaan and Tiger in the same frame, goosebumps are guaranteed! Watch them in action with the Pathaan x Tiger theme, video out now!

About YRF Spy Universe: 
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise. 

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali! 

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

snippet.description:
HealthySummerladduRecipe  #summerladduRecipe   Healthy summer laddu Recipe  which is Immunity booster ladoo recipe. summers special immunity boost laddu jo banaye aapko healthy and fit, coconut and dry fruits laddu. summers special healthy and tasty laddu jo ki hai coconut and dry fruits laddu. easy and tasty laddu recipe khaas garmiyon ke liye. garmiyon me khaas thandak dene vale laddu learn  how to make coconut and dry fruits laddu.Laddu for strength immunity and reducing headache.

#laddurecipe #healthyladdurecipe #ladoorecipe #laddu #ladoo #laddoorecipe #healthyladdu #proteinladdu #weightlosssnack #weightlossrecipe #coconutladoo

📕 https://www.youtube.com/CookWithParul/ 
📙 https://www.instagram.com/cookwithparul/  
#cookwithparul #cookwithparulrecipe 

Ingredients List: 🍕🍣 सामग्री 
🌐  Full Written Recipe🍕 Step by Step Visit my Website  https://cookwithparul.com/ 
🌐  पूरी लिखित रेसिपी 🍣 देखने के लिए आप मेरी हिंदी वेबसाइट लिंक को क्लिक कीजिये  Hindi Website  https://cookwithparul.com/hi/
* Lotus Seeds/Fox Nuts/Phool Makhana - 25 gm
* Musk Melon Seeds - 1/2 cup
* Almonds बादाम - 1/4 cup
* Cashew nut काजू - 1/4 cup
* Dates खजूर - 1/2 cup
* Clarified Butter घी - 2 tbsp
* Black Pepper Powder काली मिर्च पाउडर - 1/4 tsp
* Desiccated Coconut - 2 cup
* Cardamom Powder इलाइची - 1/2 tsp
* Mishri मिश्री - 1 cup
* Water पानी - 3/4 cup
* Pistachio पिस्ता - 1 tbsp

snippet.title: The Song Of Scorpions - Official Trailer | Irrfan Khan | Golshifteh Farahani | Anup Singh
snippet.description:
The Song of Scorpions is a story of twisted love, revenge and the redemptive power of a song. Nooran, carefree and defiantly independent, is a tribal woman learning the ancient art of healing from her grandmother, a revered scorpion-singer. When Aadam, a camel trader in the Rajasthan desert, hears her sing, he falls desperately in love. But even before they can get to know each other better, Nooran is poisoned by a treachery that sets her on a perilous journey to avenge herself and find her song.

#TheSongOfScorpions Official Trailer out now.
In Cinemas 28th April 2023.

#irrfankhan #golshiftehfarahani 

Panorama Spotlight and 70MM Talkies Present
A Feather Light Films and KNM Production 

A Film by Anup Singh

Credits:

Written And Directed By Anup Singh 

Starring: Irrfan Khan, Golshifteh Farahani, Waheeda Rehman, Shashank Arora, Tillotama Shome

Produced by Saskia Vischer, Gyan Shahaf Peled, Michel Merkt
In Co Production With: Cine Sud Promotions, Aurora Media
Co-Producers: Thierry Lenouvel, Rakesh Mehra, Zeeshan Ahmad, Shivv Sharma

Executive Producer: Justin Deimen, Gin Kai Chan 
Associate Producer: Varun Gupta

Cinematographer: Pietro Zuercher 
Editor: Marie Pierre Frappier

Original Music By Beatrice Thiriet

snippet.description:
Synopsis: Salman Bhai हैं किस किसकी जान?
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
Salman Khan along with his co-actor Pooja Hegde makes a royal entry on the sets in between the full shouting of the audience. Kapil praises Salman's new film 'Kisi Ke Bhai Kisi Ki Jaan' and his role in Pathan. He also mentions the huge fan following of Salman Khan. Then they had a fun-filled conversation about the ice cream candies. How will Kapil entertain them, Watch the episode and know more!!

FULL VIDEO | RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part -485 | Kya Balram Pakadd Paayenge Hanuman Ji Ko? #starbharat 

FULL VIDEO | RadhaKrishn Raasleela Part -485 | Kya Balram Pakadd Paayenge Hanuman Ji Ko? #starbharat
►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

#radhakrishna #sumallika #mallikasingh #radha

#nelson #redinkingsley #avcinemaawards #vikatanawards #cinemavikatan #Vikatancinemaawards  

Welcome to the prestigious Vikatan Cinema Awards Function! This annual event celebrates excellence in the world of cinema, with awards being presented to the best of the best in Tamil cinema over the past three years - 2020, 2021, and 2022. Join us as we recognize the outstanding achievements of our talented actors, actresses, directors, and technicians, who have captivated audiences with their exceptional work. The awards ceremony promises to be an unforgettable evening, filled with glamour, excitement, and emotion. Watch as the winners are announced and receive their awards from our esteemed presenters. From Best Actor and Best Actress to Best Director and Best Music Director, the competition is fierce and the talent is exceptional. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy the show as we celebrate the magic of cinema and honour the best of the best at the Vikatan Cinema Awards Function.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3748 - 18 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3748: Sihayi Hatane Ka Idea
--------------------------------------------------------
To find out more about Babita Ji's car, Bagha phones Dolly, Rustom's assistant. When Bagha asks Dolly what hue the car is, she reveals that it is red. Bagha advises Jetha to create a replica coupon and submit it to the Ramsang company despite Jetha's brooding about the broken coupon. Jetha calls Taarak to get advice on creating a fake coupon. As an alternative, Taarak offers suggestions for ink removal. Will Jetha, therefore, be able to obtain a fresh forgery of a coupon, or will he be able to remove the ink? Remain tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3748, 18 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000217162

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Dating A Cafe Owner Ft. Twarita Nagar, Usmaan | Hasley India Originals!
snippet.description:
Sign up on FairPlay: FairPlay.co.in

 Pehli nazar mei kaisa jaadu kar diya,
Tera ban baitha hai mera jiya!!!

Pehli nazar ka pyaar or Love at first sight is often considered to be an eternal truth for most of the relationships jahan ek jhalak mei hi pata lag jaata hai ki humein apna life partner mil gaya!
Kya hoga agar aap and ek din kisi cafe mei jao aur aapko apna pehli nazar wala pyar randomly wahan miljaaye? And on top of that He/She is the owner of the cafe!
Ek aisi hi anokhi jodi ki mulaqaat hui ek cafe mei jahan do dil mile aur baat ban gayi!

Watch the video till the end to know what goes on when you start dating a cafe owner.

Farq Last Episode - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 18th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3747 - 17 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3747: Babita Ka License
--------------------------------------------------------
To keep Rustom and Babita from knowing the truth, Bagha implements Bawri's suggestion. Jethalal tells Rustom ji that he will get the coupon in the evening as the winner has gone to the temple to seek blessings. Babita clicks a photograph with Rustom Ji and the coupon. Babita obtaining an automobile is a big deal to Mahila Mandal. How would everyone respond once they discover Jethalal's lies? Watch the episode to know more.


Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3747, 17 Apr 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: 1 Year For KGF Chapter 2 | Yash | Prashanth Neel | Vijay Kiragandur | Sanjay Dutt | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
One year ago today, #KGFChapter2 took us on an unforgettable journey filled with breathtaking action, intense emotions and larger-than-life characters. The film's release was nothing short of a festival, with fans celebrating in theaters around the world. We're humbled by the incredible response to the film and grateful to everyone who made it such a success. Here's to the power of storytelling and the magic of cinema!

#1ROCKYingYearOfKGF2

Written and Directed by Prashanth Neel
Produced by Vijay Kiragandur under the Banner "Hombale Films".
Starring: Rocking Star Yash, Sanjay Dutt, Srinidhi Shetty, Raveena Tandon, Prakash Raj, Malvika Avinash, Achyuth Kumar, Ayyappa P. Sharma, Rao Ramesh, Eshwari Rao, Archana Jois, T. S. About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
aarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Allu Arha as Prince Bharata - Telugu Promo | Shaakuntalam | Samantha | Gunasekhar| Dil Raju
snippet.description:
Shaakuntalam Movie also in 3D, Written & Directed by Gunasekhar, Presented by Dil Raju under Sri Venkateswara Creations in collaboration with Gunaa Teamworks, Produced by Neelima Guna.

The massively mounted film Shaakuntalam based on internationally acclaimed Kalidasa’s Sanskrit play ‘Abhijnana Shakuntalam’ is all set to release in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam & Kannada.  The story of Shaakuntalam revolves around the epic love story of Shakuntala and King Dushyant from Mahabharata, portrayed by Samantha and Dev Mohan.

The film is helmed by supremely proficient, Director Gunasekhar and marks a whimsical tale of love set in the Kashyapa Kanumalu (Kashmir), the grandeur and splendour of Dushyant’s Puru Dynasty making the film extremely exceptional.

Cast and Crew Details: 

Shaakuntalam starring Samantha, Dev Mohan, Allu Arha, Sachin Khedekar, Kabir Bedi, Dr.M Mohan Babu, Prakash Raj, Madhubala, Gautami, Aditi Balan, Ananya Nagalla, Jisshu Sengupta and others

A Film By Gunasekhar
Producer: Neelima Guna
Presentor: Dil Raju
Music: ManiSharma
Editor: Prawin Pudi
Cinematography: Shekar V Joseph
Art: Ashok
VFX Supervisor: Alagarsamy Mayan
Lyrics: Chaitanya Prasad & Shreemani
Choreography: Raju Sundaram
Action: Venkat, King Solomon
Executive Producer: Kommineni Venkateswara Rao, Hemambar Jasti
Line Producer: Yashwanth
Dialogues: Sai Madhav Burra
Costume Designer: Neeta Lulla
DI: Annapurna Studios 
Colorist : Shiva Kumar
PRO: Vamsi Kaka
Publicity Designs: Anil & Bhanu

snippet.title: Aryan ने सुन ली Lovely की बातचीत! | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 686
snippet.description:
Aryan ने सुन ली Lovely की बातचीत! | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 686

Lovely is delighted after she succeeds in concealing her identity from Tina. But her fake identity once again comes under threat when Aryan overhears her conversation and turns suspicious. Will Aryan put an end to Lovely's theatrics?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: மதுரை பரோட்டா சால்னா | Madurai Famous Parotta Salna Recipe | CDK 1179 | Chef Deena's Kitchen
snippet.description:
Parotta Salna
INGREDIENTS  

Groundnut Oil – 400 ml
Shallots – ½ Kg
Green Chilli – 20 Nos
Whole Garam Mixed (Bay Leaf, Cinnamon Sticks, Cloves, Kalpasi, Cardamom – 15gm)
Ginger Paste – 1 Ladle
Garlic Paste – 3 Ladle
Country Tomato – 500 G
Mint – 2 Hand Full
Coriander – 1 Hand Full
Mutton With Bones – 1 Kg
Mutton Fat – 200 G
Curry Leaves  - As Required 
Turmeric Powder  - 3 Tsp
Cumin Powder – 3 Ladle
Fennel Powder – 2 Tsp
Pepper Powder – 5 Tsp
 Coriander Powder – 1 Ladle
Red Chilli Powder – ½ Ladle
Chilli Powder – 1 Ladle
Salt – As Required
Coconut – 8 Nos
Peanut – 50 G
Roasted Channa – 50 G
Coconut Milk – 1 Ladle
Nutmeg Powder – ½ piece

Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats. 

Subscribe to Chef Deena Cooks (CDK) for more cooking videos.

Dhyan Sreenivasan is an Indian actor, and film director who works in Malayalam films.Dhyan Sreenivasan was born on December 20, 1988 in Thalassery, Kerala, India. Dhyan Sreenivasan made his acting debut with Thira, directed by Dhyan Sreenivasan elder brother Vineeth Sreenivasan. Dhyan is the younger son of noted actor and screenwriter Sreenivasan. Dhyan Sreenivasan brother Vineeth Sreenivasan is a singer, actor and director who also works in Malayalam cinema. Dhyan married his longtime girlfriend Arpita Sebastian on 7 April 2017. He made his film debut with the Malayalam film Thira which has Shobana in main lead role. In the film, Dhyan Sreenivasan did a supporting role along with two-time National Award winning actress Shobana. His performance in the film was generally well-received by critics and the audience.
